package logsink

// Package logsink defines a worker which provides access to a logger which
// records log entries generated by artefacts running in each model.
//
// The source of log records for each model includes:
// - machine and unit agents
// - model workers
//
// The destination of the log records is a log file in the models subdirectory
// under /var/log/juju.
